<subSubSection pageId="6" pageNumber="101" type="reference_group">
<paragraph pageId="6" pageNumber="101">Species identification confirmed by RSA, 2015</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection pageId="6" pageNumber="101" type="notes">
<paragraph pageId="6" pageNumber="101">Note.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="6" pageNumber="101">
<bibRefCitation author="Bousquet, Y" journalOrPublisher="Pensoft, Sofia" pageId="9" pageNumber="104" title="Checklist of Beetles of Canada and Alaska. Second edition." year="2013">Bousquet et al. (2013)</bibRefCitation>
listed this species without providing any details on its distribution in Canada, based on a similar inclusion in 
<bibRefCitation author="O'Brien, CW" journalOrPublisher="Memoirs of the American Entomological Institute" pageId="11" pageNumber="106" pagination="1 - 382" title="Annotated checklist of the weevils (Curculionidae sensu lato) of North America, Central America, and the West Indies (Coleoptera: Curculionoidea)" volume="34" year="1982">
<normalizedToken originalValue="O’Brien">O'Brien</normalizedToken>
and Wibmer (1982)
</bibRefCitation>
. We provide specific locality data for Canada for the first time. Like other 
<taxonomicName class="Insecta" family="Curculionidae" genus="Lixus" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Lixus" order="Coleoptera" pageId="6" pageNumber="101" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">Lixus</taxonomicName>
Fabricius, 1801 spp., this species is probably associated with 
<taxonomicName class="Magnoliopsida" family="Polygonaceae" genus="Polygonum" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="Polygonum" order="Caryophyllales" pageId="6" pageNumber="101" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="genus">Polygonum</taxonomicName>
spp. (
<taxonomicName family="Polygonaceae" lsidName="" pageId="6" pageNumber="101" rank="family">Polygonaceae</taxonomicName>
). Numerous CMNC specimens from Texas were collected on 
<taxonomicName class="Magnoliopsida" family="Polygonaceae" genus="Polygonum" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="Polygonum" order="Caryophyllales" pageId="6" pageNumber="101" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="genus">Polygonum</taxonomicName>
.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
