<taxonomicName class="Magnoliopsida" family="Asteraceae" genus="Bidens" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="Bidens cernua" order="Asterales" pageId="6" pageNumber="101" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="cernua">Bidens cernua</taxonomicName>
, P. de Tonnancour (1, CPTO).
</paragraph>
